 +// Company:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +// Engineer:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Create Date: 2023/05/10 20:36:05                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 +// Design Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Module Name: DataMemory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +// Project Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +// Target Devices:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Tool Versions:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +// Description:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Dependencies:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Revision:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +// Revision 0.01 - File Created                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Additional Comments:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +module DataMemory(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    input clk,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    input [31:0] address,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    input [31:0] writeData,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +    input MemWrite,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 +    input MemRead,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    output reg [31:0] readData                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    reg [31:0] memory [0:1023];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    always @(posedge clk) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +        if (MemWrite) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +            memory[address[11:2]] <= writeData;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +        end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    always @(*) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 +        if (MemRead) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +            readData = memory[address[11:2]];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 +        end else begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +            readData = 32'b0;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 +        end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +endmodule                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +End File# Aaronlcj/MIPS-CPU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 +`timescale 1ns / 1ps                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Company:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +// Engineer:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Create Date: 2023/05/10 20:36:05                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 +// Design Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Module Name: InstructionMemory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +// Project Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +// Target Devices:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Tool Versions:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +// Description:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Dependencies:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Revision:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +// Revision 0.01 - File Created                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Additional Comments:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +module InstructionMemory(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    input [31:0] address,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    output reg [31:0] instruction                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    reg [31:0] memory [0:1023];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    initial begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +        $readmemh("instructions.mem", memory);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    always @(*) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 +        instruction = memory[address[11:2]];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +endmodule                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +End File# Aaronlcj/MIPS-CPU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 +# MIPS-CPU/MIPS-CPU.srcs/sources_1/new/MIPS_CPU.v                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +`timescale 1ns / 1ps                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Company:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +// Engineer:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Create Date: 2023/05/10 20:36:05                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 +// Design Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Module Name: MIPS_CPU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +// Project Name:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +// Target Devices:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Tool Versions:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +// Description:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Dependencies:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +// Revision:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +// Revision 0.01 - File Created                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +// Additional Comments:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +//                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +module MIPS_CPU(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    input clk,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    input reset                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // PC                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    reg [31:0] PC;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    wire [31:0] PC_next;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +    wire [31:0] PC_plus_4;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire [31:0] PC_branch;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire [31:0] PC_jump;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +    wire PCSrc;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Instruction Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    wire [31:0] instruction;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    wire RegDst;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    wire Jump;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    wire Branch;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    wire MemRead;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +    wire MemtoReg;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    wire [1:0] ALUOp;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 +    wire MemWrite;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    wire ALUSrc;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    wire RegWrite;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Register File                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +    wire [4:0] writeReg;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +    wire [31:0] writeData;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire [31:0] readData1;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire [31:0] readData2;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // ALU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire [3:0] ALUCtr;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +    wire [31:0] ALUResult;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +    wire zero;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    wire [31:0] ALUInput2;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Data Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    wire [31:0] readData;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Sign Extend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    wire [31:0] signExtImm;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // PC update                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    assign PC_plus_4 = PC + 4;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    assign PC_branch = PC_plus_4 + (signExtImm << 2);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 +    assign PC_jump = {PC_plus_4[31:28], instruction[25:0], 2'b00};                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    assign PCSrc = Branch & zero;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +    assign PC_next = Jump ? PC_jump : (PCSrc ? PC_branch : PC_plus_4);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    always @(posedge clk or posedge reset) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +        if (reset) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +            PC <= 32'b0;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +        end else begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +            PC <= PC_next;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +        end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Instruction Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +    InstructionMemory im(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 +        .address(PC),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 +        .instruction(instruction)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +    Control ctrl(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 +        .opcode(instruction[31:26]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +        .RegDst(RegDst),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +        .Jump(Jump),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +        .Branch(Branch),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +        .MemRead(MemRead),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 +        .MemtoReg(MemtoReg),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +        .ALUOp(ALUOp),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +        .MemWrite(MemWrite),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +        .ALUSrc(ALUSrc),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 +        .RegWrite(RegWrite)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Register File                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +    assign writeReg = RegDst ? instruction[15:11] : instruction[20:16];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +    assign writeData = MemtoReg ? readData : ALUResult;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    RegisterFile rf(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 +        .clk(clk),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +        .readReg1(instruction[25:21]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +        .readReg2(instruction[20:16]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +        .writeReg(writeReg),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +        .writeData(writeData),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +        .RegWrite(RegWrite),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 +        .readData1(readData1),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 +        .readData2(readData2)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 +    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // Sign Extend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    assign signExtImm = {{16{instruction[15]}}, instruction[15:0]};                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 +                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 +    // ALU Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 +    ALUControl aluCtrl(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 +        .ALUOp(ALUOp),
