 -module MIPS_CPU(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    input clk,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    input reset                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // PC                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -    reg [31:0] PC;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    wire [31:0] PC_next;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -    wire [31:0] PC_plus_4;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire [31:0] PC_branch;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire [31:0] PC_jump;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -    wire PCSrc;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Instruction Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -    wire [31:0] instruction;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    wire RegDst;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    wire Jump;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    wire Branch;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    wire MemRead;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 -    wire MemtoReg;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    wire [1:0] ALUOp;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 -    wire MemWrite;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    wire ALUSrc;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    wire RegWrite;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Register File                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 -    wire [4:0] writeReg;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -    wire [31:0] writeData;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire [31:0] readData1;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire [31:0] readData2;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // ALU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire [3:0] ALUCtr;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -    wire [31:0] ALUResult;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    wire zero;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    wire [31:0] ALUInput2;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Data Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    wire [31:0] readData;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Sign Extend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    wire [31:0] signExtImm;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // PC update                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    assign PC_plus_4 = PC + 4;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    assign PC_branch = PC_plus_4 + (signExtImm << 2);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 -    assign PC_jump = {PC_plus_4[31:28], instruction[25:0], 2'b00};                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    assign PCSrc = Branch & zero;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 -    assign PC_next = Jump ? PC_jump : (PCSrc ? PC_branch : PC_plus_4);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    always @(posedge clk or posedge reset) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -        if (reset) begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -            PC <= 32'b0;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -        end else begin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -            PC <= PC_next;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -        end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 -    end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Instruction Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -    InstructionMemory im(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -        .address(PC),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
 -        .instruction(instruction)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -    Control ctrl(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 -        .opcode(instruction[31:26]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 -        .RegDst(RegDst),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -        .Jump(Jump),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 -        .Branch(Branch),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -        .MemRead(MemRead),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -        .MemtoReg(MemtoReg),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .ALUOp(ALUOp),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .MemWrite(MemWrite),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .ALUSrc(ALUSrc),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 -        .RegWrite(RegWrite)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Register File                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 -    assign writeReg = RegDst ? instruction[15:11] : instruction[20:16];                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -    assign writeData = MemtoReg ? readData : ALUResult;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    RegisterFile rf(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
 -        .clk(clk),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -        .readReg1(instruction[25:21]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .readReg2(instruction[20:16]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .writeReg(writeReg),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .writeData(writeData),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -        .RegWrite(RegWrite),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .readData1(readData1),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -        .readData2(readData2)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Sign Extend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    assign signExtImm = {{16{instruction[15]}}, instruction[15:0]};                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // ALU Control                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    ALUControl aluCtrl(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -        .ALUOp(ALUOp),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .funct(instruction[5:0]),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 -        .ALUCtr(ALUCtr)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // ALU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -    assign ALUInput2 = ALUSrc ? signExtImm : readData2;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    ALU alu(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .A(readData1),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .B(ALUInput2),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .ALUOp(ALUCtr),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
 -        .C(ALUResult),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -        .zero(zero)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 -    // Data Memory                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -    DataMemory dm(                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -        .clk(clk),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
 -        .address(ALUResult),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .writeData(readData2),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 -        .MemWrite(MemWrite),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
 -        .MemRead(MemRead),                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
 -        .readData(readData)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
 -    );                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 -endmodule                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
 -End File# Aaronlcj/MIPS-CPU
